<li><strong>Expanding DApp Possibilities:</strong> By enabling cross-chain communication, Cardano opens up new possibilities for DApp development. Developers can now create applications that can interact with different chains, accessing a wider range of functionalities and resources. This expands the potential use cases and utility of DApps built on Cardano.</li>
</ul>



