<p>Cardano DApp development has been facilitated by the availability of frameworks and tools specifically designed for the platform. These frameworks, such as Plutus and Marlowe, provide developers with the necessary tools and resources to create smart contracts and build complex applications on the Cardano blockchain.</p>



<p>As a result, Cardano has seen an increase in the number of DApps being developed and deployed on its platform. This surge in popularity is further fueled by the growing interest in cryptocurrencies and the potential for innovation in the blockchain space.</p>



<p>As the Cardano ecosystem continues to evolve, we can expect to see even more exciting DApps being developed on the platform, further solidifying Cardano&#8217;s position in the crypto world.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Breakdown of Top Performing DApps on ADA</h3>



