<li><strong>Responsiveness</strong>: Build DApps with responsive design, supporting a wide range of devices, preempting user needs for on-the-go access to Cardano DeFi services.</li>



<li><strong>Interoperability</strong>: Using the Plutus smart contract platform, integrate with other systems to provide a cohesive experience while maintaining robust security.</li>



