<p>This includes exploring the underlying infrastructure of Cardano, such as its multi-layered architecture and its use of the Haskell programming language.</p>



<p>Additionally, understanding the role of smart contracts and the Cardano Settlement Layer (CSL) in DApp integration is essential for developers and users alike.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">The Foundation of Cardano&#8217;s DApp Landscape</h3>



<p>The integration of DApps into Cardano&#8217;s ecosystem requires a comprehensive understanding of its foundation.</p>



<p>Cardano&#8217;s DApp ecosystem is built on a strong foundation that prioritizes user experience, security, performance, and innovation.</p>



