<p>These frameworks enable developers to leverage the unique features of Cardano&#8217;s blockchain, such as its scalability and interoperability. Security is a top priority in Cardano&#8217;s DApp landscape, with the use of formal verification methods and rigorous auditing processes.</p>



<p>Additionally, Cardano&#8217;s performance is optimized through its layered architecture and consensus protocol.</p>



<p>The ecosystem fosters innovation by actively encouraging collaboration, research, and experimentation.</p>



